      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="edit_discussion_settings" data-step-uuid="9cc63049-7090-45fa-b0c9-cfc02eb55f48">
    <h2 id="edit_discussion_settings" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Edit Discussion Settings</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/004/964/780/original/6511fe9c-0212-4cc2-94c4-e656aa4bfd2b.png" srcset="" alt="Edit Discussion Settings" height="499" width="354">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_71c6028a-c67a-41d4-a5bd-d55462988dfb" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Check the <strong>Create discussion topics </strong>checkbox [1]. To allow students to create anonymous course discussions, click the <strong>Create anonymous discussion topics</strong> checkbox [2]. </p>
<p>To save discussion settings, click the <strong>Save Settings</strong> button [3].</p>
